Description
-----------

The mask\_lfe keywork only allows sound from the shader to be outbut through the LFE (subwoofer) surround sound speaker in a 5.1 setup.

Usage
-----

`mask_lfe`

Example
-------

`ship_engine_rumble`
`{`
`   mindistance 100`
`   maxdistance 1000`
`   volume 10`
`   looping`
`   mask_backleft`
`   shakes .1`
`   sound/last_stand/loop_rumble_LFE_b.wav`
`}`

Notes
-----

When this is in use, sound only comes from that channel when 5.1 surround is used. If you use 2 channel (stereo) sound the channel will be muted and this sound will not be played.

